14:07.368 --> 14:17.042
The weeping prophet who battled with loneliness and insecurity and literally the prophet of God cursed the day

14:18.434 --> 14:19.055
He was born.

14:21.877 --> 14:29.525
So, if you find yourself in a compromised place, mentally, emotionally, you're challenged.

14:29.545 --> 14:32.388
Christians will often say, you just need more faith.

14:34.010 --> 14:34.971
