14:41.638 --> 14:42.659
We always need faith.

14:42.899 --> 14:46.002
And we always need God, but you're a holistic,

14:46.082 --> 14:49.086
being, spirit, soul, and body.

14:49.106 --> 15:02.085
So you may need more God and you may need a nap and a Snickers bar or a nap and a protein bar because you're not eating a Snickers bar even more.

15:02.145 --> 15:11.378
Even though there's some good commercial, but you're getting a protein bar because you're not just strong in the spirit, but you're strong in your body.

15:12.962 --> 15:15.305
I'm just making some of this stuff as I go to just work with you.

15:15.325 --> 15:17.006
I got a plan, but some of it just comes out.

15:17.066 --> 15:17.547
So you never know.

15:17.927 --> 15:28.759
So you need more God and you may need different friends because bad company corrupts good character.

15:29.660 --> 15:32.844
Walk with a wise and become wise to compare you with fool, suffer harm.

15:33.464 --> 15:34.105
Well, I'm hurting.

