15:37.709 --> 15:42.514
Maybe you need more God and you need to maybe change your diet or

15:42.818 --> 15:49.828
Talk to a doctor because your hormones are out of lack, or you've got a chemical imbalance, or you may need to talk to a counselor or to a pastor.

15:50.570 --> 15:59.743
Yeah, you need more God, but when we're talking about mental health, God looks at us holistically, spirit, soul, and body.

15:59.763 --> 16:02.207
So all healing starts with God.

16:02.928 --> 16:04.530
All healing comes from God.

16:05.171 --> 16:12.242
All healing, we give the glory to God, but God will often direct us, not just spiritually, but sometimes our mind, our will, our motion,

16:12.322 --> 16:19.572
And sometimes even in our body, what I want you to hear is that God cares about you and He cares about all of you, every part of you, every part of you.

16:19.973 --> 16:22.577
